body: And don't worry, that was me last week, I was just stopping by to say hi and enjoy some good old memories
Hey buddy, long time no see! I'm as cosmic as ever so everything is fine, my people needed me in other cosmic places and also some things I had to take care of so that's why I wasn't here too much

Onii-chan? Onnniii-chaaan!!! *said in anime girl voice* 😭😭😭 it's been so long, where have you been my comrade? I saw you comment last week but I couldn't believe it was really you after such a long time, I thought it might of been a sus imposter 😅 how have you been?
